metadata.name: Dollar 4 Dollar
metadata.description:
Celebrate with us, this historic moment in history. 

"I was doing the math yesterday, on the Bored Apes collection, and granted Moonbirds as a percentage is down more than apes is, but in terms of a dollar amount, apes is down more than Moonbirds. Meaning if you had bought the peak of Bored Apes, and you held today, dollar for dollar, you would have lost more."
